  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395920/extras/5039afe6d01d70c5fc8cab5ec6f01972.webp?t=1751085473\" width=296 height=40 /></span><br><br><br>GrappleWell is a physics based rage game that will have you climbing up from the bottom of a well.<br><br>You, (as a coin who been thrown down a well) naturally can only move via grapple hook, but beware, grapples are not an infinite resource! they recharge quickly while you are touching the ground and slowly in the air.<br><br>Many a young coin has tried and failed to escape the dreaded well, could your tale be one of legends?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395920/extras/c04594b2fa591abf97302fde2464ec61.poster.avif?t=1751085473\" width=800 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395920/extras/c04594b2fa591abf97302fde2464ec61.webm?t=1751085473\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395920/extras/c04594b2fa591abf97302fde2464ec61.mp4?t=1751085473\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395920/extras/5039afe6d01d70c5fc8cab5ec6f01972.webp?t=1751085473\" width=296 height=40 /></span><br><br><br>GrappleWell is a physics based rage game that will have you climbing up from the bottom of a well.<br><br>You, (as a coin who been thrown down a well) naturally can only move via grapple hook, but beware, grapples are not an infinite resource! they recharge quickly while you are touching the ground and slowly in the air.<br><br>Many a young coin has tried and failed to escape the dreaded well, could your tale be one of legends?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395920/extras/c04594b2fa591abf97302fde2464ec61.poster.avif?t=1751085473\" width=800 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395920/extras/c04594b2fa591abf97302fde2464ec61.webm?t=1751085473\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395920/extras/c04594b2fa591abf97302fde2464ec61.mp4?t=1751085473\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
